events.name: Jumpstarters 2012
events.about:
ilab’s Jumpstart 2012 event is a weekend-long festival of innovation, to be held September 28th – 30th. Teams of between 2 to 6 individuals will compete to demonstrate a new product or service for our judging panel, with the winner to receive a support package worth $20,000 from ilab to help commercialise their product and jumpstart their business.

Participation in Jumpstart 2012 is open to individuals as well as existing teams; individuals will be asked to form teams either before or during the introductory session on Friday September 28th. You can read more about our judges, the prizes, as well as terms & conditions of the contest.
